window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Bishop</b><br> <br> She was broken by the hands of my own father.<br> <br> I can’t hide in the shadows anymore, watching her from a safe distance.<br> It’s time to show her all my plays.<br> <br> Kiara Coleman has the answers I need, and if I have to drag her back into my dark world to get them, I will.<br> <br> Once she’s there I’ll do everything I can to put her broken pieces back together again and keep her in her rightful place by my side.<br> <br> <b>Kiara</b><br> <br> I escaped my living hell three years ago.<br> I’ve learned to mask the pain and hide from the nightmares that taunt me.<br> <br> I won a scholarship that will change my life, I should be happy about being here. A fresh start.<br> <br> Except this fresh start puts me right into the path of him.<br> Bishop Murdoch, the son of the monster I’ve spent the last three years trying to outrun.<br> <br> <b>Author's Note:</b> <i>Please be aware that there is some content that may be disturbing for some listeners. Trigger warnings are included at the beginning of this audiobook.</i></p>"; 
